    <h2>Information in Peptipedia</h2>
    <br>
    <p>Our database has 92055 registered and characterized peptides, currently the peptide database with the most extensive registrations to date. According to our system of categories proposed in this work, we classify peptides, suggesting ten main categories. Each of them has subcategories or different levels of classification, according to previously reported activities. Remarkably,  we generate our platform's database system, integrating the information from 30 previously reported repositories or tools.</p>
