<div class="row">
  <div class="col-lg-6">
    <h2>Peptide moonlight</h2>
    <br>
    <p>Peptides are relevant due to their magnetic therapeutic properties and their applications in the field of biotechnology. Many peptides have different activities at the same time. That is, they can have a therapeutic role, and they can also have signal peptide activity. In a simple way, we analyze the relationships of dependence or mutuality of information between peptides, where activities are sought simultaneously, and how they are related. It is interesting to demonstrate that signal and sensory peptides are related to therapeutic peptides.</p>
  </div>
